        "title": "fix(agents): load bootstrap files from agentDir alongside workspace",
        "body": "## Problem\nBootstrap files configured in `agentDir` were not loaded alongside workspace bootstrap files, causing missing context when both workspace and agentDir have bootstrap files.\n\n## Fix\nLoad explicitly configured `agentDir` bootstrap files alongside workspace files. AgentDir files override same-named workspace files.\n\n## Real Behavior Proof\n\n### Test Results (vitest 4.1.8)\n```\n✓ src/agents/bootstrap-files.test.ts (37 tests, 100% pass)\n```\n\n### Behavior addressed\nAgents with `agentDir` configured now have their bootstrap files loaded alongside workspace bootstrap files.\n\n### Evidence after fix\nAll 37 bootstrap-files tests pass, covering workspace + agentDir bootstrap loading, file ordering, and override behavior.\n",
